# PHYSICS::ROPE_SET_REFFRAMEVELOCITY_COLLIDERORDER

## Summary
0 - don't set ref frame velocity , 1 - set ref frame velocity A to B, 2 - ref frame velocity B to A

## Parameters
* **ROPE_INDEX** ropeID
* **INT** colliderOrder
